PREAMBLE
--------
To create a bot (or something along those lines) that scrapes a configured Telegram channel for links pointing to movies/television shows/documentaries from the following URLs:
* imdb
* wikipedia

Scraped links are to be stored in DB after tagged with the following details:
* year
* genre
* cast
* crew

A user should be able to query the bot on one or more tags in any particular order to display results accordingly.
